{
  "texts": [
    "We pre-train the model on synthetic 3-D trajectories, and fine-tune its weights on real eye-tracking datasets -both sources of data are discussed next.",
    "We now describe the datasets and evaluation protocols used for scanpath prediction.",
    "To better reflect real-world reading scenarios, we selected diverse benchmark datasets and adopted multiple evaluation settings, including three distinct data-splitting approaches.",
    "Further details on the data and evaluation metrics are in appendix A.1.",
    "As illustrated in Figure 1, we pre-train ScanEZ on E-Z Reader simulations, which were generated by Sood et al. (2020) from the CNN and Daily Mail corpus (Hermann et al., 2015)."
  ]
}